Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:23.21,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}褪色的景致 随着风儿逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:31.01,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,往日记忆 悄悄苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:37.93,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,走在熟悉的路上却无法回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}最初的谎言 最后的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:57.45,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那天许下的誓言早已崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:04.71,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,只留下激昂虚幻的记忆碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:12.67,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们一同从这梦境中醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:18.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}这份思念 也不会被忘记 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:27.69,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}怀念的往昔照亮今天的我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:21.86,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那时还年幼的我 抬头仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:28.28,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,发现天空真的很辽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:32.74,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的人 用双手保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:38.67,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经认真的这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:50.14,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有长高 我为此而悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.43,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾无数次伸展手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:23:00.78,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,却还是无法触及 那无比宽广的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:06.69,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却没有一丝怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:11.62,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,始终坚信那美好的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:14.91,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾有过悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:22.29,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,亦会忍不住落下 大滴大滴的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:33.39,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}但是我坚信 那时我的眼中有着无比的光辉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛忽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像迫使你们作出了不愉快的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然你们想找诺鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该知道那里迟早会成为必经之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全被你看穿了么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之德·希耶罗对你们来说是个重要的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是碰巧啊 碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然对我们补陀落来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是通往Great Wall所必经的荡涤灵魂之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对所有造访者来说 那里也同时是抉择之门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉择之门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paper Moon Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全系统进入停泊状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂魄干涉器的状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定位系统不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在这么显眼的地方反正也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎一直保持点火 随时可以起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不准备在这儿久留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他也想尽快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下那老婆婆之后 我想一定很快就会走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没忘带什么东西吧 再确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 虽然不成敬意…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有一天会用得着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时要是没有的话会很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿不会碰上用得着它的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿无上的光明等候着各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 多吉哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 终于做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的新滑空板 帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 也不知道帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完这个就起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兰德这么说的 有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兰德? 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的波浪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兰德说过只要有好波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪里都会去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兰德还真是反覆无常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆就在这里下船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就说好到这里为止的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 你去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去把滑空板拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在加水的这段时间先在这里滑滑空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没变化 现在正在补给饮用水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成之后立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了这么好的波浪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对只为波浪而生的你来说真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又算怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 有意见么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 霍兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 只是你不去滑空么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑空?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个家伙可已经先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 霍兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的波浪真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么好的滑空点居然什么人也没有 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对、对不起 水还没加完…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里的波浪很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次见到这么棒的波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这废墟也有利波浪的形成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道为什么没人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真想感谢上苍造出了这么好的滑空点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛莫名其妙就打我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有个理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 莫名其妙地连打两次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈脸色好难看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为姐姐惹妈妈生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 是因为林克尿床了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没尿床呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 兰顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木炭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很新
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 最近才受过轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兰德 兰顿他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗 那可真是灾难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得奇怪么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里外表看来虽然只是房车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但里面其实却是修道场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修道场?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补陀落真的是反政府组织么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为学校的老师和同学都说不知道你们想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你们是可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白不了解的东西就是可怕的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点大家都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老婆婆看起来却完全不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 光看外表是无法了解一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是只看外表的话并没有很大差异
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果大家都能理解这一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也不会变成这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块古老的土地并不仅仅属于人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我们却在不稳定的珊瑚岩中打入无数桩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图压制它们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是课本上说如果不打桩固定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会发生地壳变动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么打桩固定之后就不会发生地壳变动了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是囫囵吞枣地读着某些人所展示的东西罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没找到么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在天黑之前回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且尼尔瓦修在这里很危险 你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么特地跑来集中在这种什么都没有的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是抉择之门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉择之门?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修达德斯·德·希耶罗 天空之都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾以美丽闻名的补陀落之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管被如何破坏 这一点都不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是该走向通往Great Wall之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是该继续停留在这大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里的人都要被驱使作出某种选择
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是座这样的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而却一片狼藉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 几年前的某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队袭击了这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们毁了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且屠杀了补陀落的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提普特里 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西又出现了 那白色恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色恶魔?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿 我知道你在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心你 快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡 来找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚 滚出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 她做错了什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人是刽子手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又曾经做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么啊 优莱卡她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我真的曾经是军队的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时轰炸要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时轰炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的空中战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军空中战舰正高速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现正在对德·希耶罗南部进行轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮座回转还没结束 无法发射主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调速轮安定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步调勉强一致了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兰德呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开909出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是去回收尼尔瓦修了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走吧 叫他别迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家要对你做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看起来都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我活该
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我活该
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被人这样对待都是我自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 竟然对女孩子做这种事 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我活该
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我曾经在这里杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歼灭这座城市的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们SOF接到的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOF? 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们所在的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的特殊部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说 难道月光州的前身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只要有命令就绝对执行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹的杀人部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 传言居然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有理由 只是纯粹地执行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我作为自己存在的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那时的我 只有尼尔瓦修和霍兰德可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 只要霍兰德说要战斗 我就去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 那时候发现的孩子们就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特尔 莫里斯 林克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 难道指挥了那场作战的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们SOF小队的队长 是霍兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 但是 那也是没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那时候在战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你又是军人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也还在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所做的不是游戏也不是运动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的战斗 人类受到伤害 甚至死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兰顿 你也在参与其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参与这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会回来么 妈妈会回来么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 现在霍兰德正去接她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 妈妈会回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 霍兰德从来没说过谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 偏偏在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决定无论用怎样的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要补偿我们所犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为此我们就首先要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须活下去完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我们会不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 优莱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了要我战斗才把我带来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为如果你不在 尼尔瓦修就不能正常运作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如果没有尼尔瓦修 我们就没法完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什么使命不使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那为什么 为什么你在这里救了梅特尔她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是全盘相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你之所以脱离军队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为不想再奉命去杀害无辜的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么使命不使命的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样不是和听命于军队没有任何区别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡 你在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意见到无辜的人被杀害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论用怎样的形式都想赎罪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在出去的话 会给霍兰德他们添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿 你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开尼尔瓦修去阻止军队的轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能对提普特里老婆婆她们见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起来吧 优莱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明什么都没做 怎么忽然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 兰顿 尼尔瓦修说让我服从兰顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然导航不管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是洞已经堵住了 数据可以在主监视器看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么办 绕过塔的话可能就赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这两座塔的中间穿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕到他们前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了 作战结束 立刻离开这一空域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 2点方向出现不明机体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,型号不明的LFO正高速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LFO? 不是RPG么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对空炮么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这就是你们的决断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算前途艰险 但祝愿你们的目的地一定充满光明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏反应引擎 削弱反射能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是优莱卡的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡 优莱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看右边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道么 这里据说是个让所有人作出选择的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 优莱卡也一定在这里选择了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 提普特里婆婆说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管这里的外表怎样改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里还是这里 不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你当初在这里作出的是个了不起的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使现在来看也同样了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这地方不会改变一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你过去选择了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也相信 你还是和当时的你一样 没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你来了之后 我可能变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 虽然不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时我却由衷地想为这女孩做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的选择 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部责任都在我 那些全都是我擅自做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以优莱卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的滑空板怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是加工过了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 慌乱中丢失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在下一块滑空板上装上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听优莱卡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要带着这轮子 你就是月光州的正式成员了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后可不准擅自行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保持整洁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这凌乱的房间是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 这是你的房间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这是你作为正式成员的首份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这房间收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没变 我没变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么 是这样吧 是吧 尼尔瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了逃避过去的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光州驶向一切开始的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里和一名少女一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一项计划正要展开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Higher Than The Sun
